    UmbraVox.App.RuntimeLog
    UmbraVox.App.Startup
    UmbraVox.Chat.Wire
    UmbraVox.Chat.Session
    UmbraVox.Chat.Message
    UmbraVox.Chat.Transaction
    UmbraVox.Chat.Contacts
    UmbraVox.Chat.API
    -- Storage
    UmbraVox.Storage.ChainDB
    UmbraVox.Storage.StateDB
    UmbraVox.Storage.Index
    UmbraVox.Storage.Checkpoint
    UmbraVox.Storage.Schema
    UmbraVox.Storage.Anthony
    -- Protocol / Serialization
    UmbraVox.Protocol.Encoding
